HEADWORD: Paramaleic
<hw>Par`a*ma*le"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>para-</ets> + <ets>maleic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, an acid obtained from malic acid,
and now called <altname>fumaric</altname> <xex>acid</xex>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

